{"tid":809170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【北海道地震】來自2066年的日本「未來人」預言　2025年關東大地震致3萬死傷","createTime":"2018-09-07T03:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T12:21:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b33bc26d66a1485b2b824e923b922d85d3ac7aac","tid":809170,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2155000/2155075/future_thumb_201712124_T_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2155000%2F2155075%2Ffuture_thumb_201712124_T_1024.jpg&h=3ec815c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日日本接連受颱風「飛燕」吹襲及北海道地震打擊，電台主持森美今早(6日)在商台節目上提及一名聲稱來自2066年的日本埼玉「未來人」，曾預言日本將面對的災難。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，該名「未來人」自稱於2036年出生，是一名30歲的大學生。他曾就日本的未來發表預言，相關內容於2016年在YouTube頻道「未来人ちゃんねる」播出。<br />\n<br />\n這位「未來人」的部份預言節錄如下：<br />\n<br />\n    日本將於2025年發生關東東海大地震，造成近3萬人死亡，程度與2011年「311大地震」相若。造成人命傷亡主要因海嘯及火災所致。<br />\n<br />\n    日本經濟自2020年東京奧運後，開始走下坡。日本政府債券制度崩壞，出現通貨膨脹。至2066年，日本經濟正在復蘇。<br />\n<br />\n    許多年輕人到海外尋求工作機會及發展，日本人才流失。<br />\n<br />\n    現時日本藝能界甚具人氣的Johnny事務所藝人、AKB48組合，未來不再存在。<br />\n<br />\n    未來仍然有「風俗店」(色情場所)。<br />\n<br />\n    新一代的人會想成為YouTuber。<br />\n<br />\n    日本成為動漫強國，但動漫師會向海外發展，因為薪金較佳。<br />\n<br />\n    海平面持續上升，約有1萬名來自帛琉的人遷往東京、沖繩等地居住。<br />\n<br />\n    人類在火星建立宇宙基地，但並非讓人住，而是用作太空行星探測。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2155075/%E3%80%90%E5%8C%97%E6%B5%B7%E9%81%93%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E3%80%91%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA2066%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8D%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80%E3%80%802025%E5%B9%B4%E9%97%9C%E6%9D%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E8%87%B43%E8%90%AC%E6%AD%BB%E5%82%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2155075%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259C%2587%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%2587%25AA2066%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E3%2580%258D%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A8%2580%25E3%2580%25802025%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%259C%2587%25E8%2587%25B43%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%2582%25B7&d=Lef8AG442bpl9RNJhf0opgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d56e7ffc\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2155075/%E3%80%90%E5%8C%97%E6%B5%B7%E9%81%93%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E3%80%91%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA2066%E5%B9%B4%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8D%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80%E3%80%802025%E5%B9%B4%E9%97%9C%E6%9D%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%9C%87%E8%87%B43%E8%90%AC%E6%AD%BB%E5%82%B7</a>"},{"pid":"e37ed98aac8fd2df3ccdf37b040bea45d0dc3220","tid":809170,"uid":85659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"通篇十足台灣糞青語氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85adb070ada26476217cbad2611ecefca573f43f","tid":809170,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:21:07.000Z","msg":"點解2016年 預測唔到2018年咁多災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a87a19526abf335c4e9ad6180e999296182a98","tid":809170,"uid":42921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"中二病"},{"pid":"1e0f9d7e5b0372dd60195a4690ae498b783984b7","tid":809170,"uid":67294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:23:22.000Z","msg":"啲預言廢到 AKB依家都收緊皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74d0cb6a44798cc6a64e68eb45926779c949876","tid":809170,"uid":51436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T03:32:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> 未來仍然有「風俗店」(色情場所)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 